                        <p align="justify">
                      <font face="Arial" size="2"><b>Toothache:</b><br>
                      Toothache because of caries in tooth may be temporarily relieved by acupressure.  The extraction of caries tooth is advisable.&nbsp;<br>
                      <br>
                      Press the following 2 points for 2-3 minutes each.<br>
                      <br>
                      <b>Point no.1</b>	-	Same as in case of headache<br>
                      <b>Point no.2</b>	-	½ Finger width distance from the web margin joining 2nd &amp; 3rd toe</font>
                      </td>
